OL,3,CCriminal investigation into disposal
OL,4,Cof ashes at crematorium
OL,6,FA criminal investigation has been
OL,7,Flaunched into a crematorium following
OL,8,Fconcerns about the disposal of ashes.
OL,10,FLincoln Council said there had been
OL,11,Fsix incidents where the burial of
OL,12,Fashes at Lincoln Crematorium had not
OL,13,Fbeen dealt with "in accordance with
OL,14,Fthe wishes of the families of the
OL,15,Fdeceased".
OL,17,FLincolnshire Police is investigating
OL,18,Fone case where it said a burial
OL,19,Fceremony went ahead even though ashes
OL,20,F"could not be located".
