OL,3,CCriminal investigation into disposal
OL,4,Cof ashes at crematorium
OL,6,FTwo men, aged 52 and 38, and a 46-year-
OL,7,Fold woman, have been arrested on
OL,8,Fsuspicion of misconduct in public
OL,9,Foffice. The men have also been
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of fraud.
OL,12,FThe council, which operates the
OL,13,Fcrematorium, has commissioned an
OL,14,Furgent inspection of the facility by
OL,15,Fthe Federation of Burial and Cremation
OL,16,FAuthorities and has launched its own
OL,17,Finternal investigation.
OL,19,FCouncil chief executive Angela Andrews
OL,20,Fsaid initial concerns were raised by a
OL,21,Fmember of council staff.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
