OL,6,FShe added: "I am shocked and
OL,7,Fdistraught to confirm that a small
OL,8,Fnumber of families did not receive the
OL,9,Flevel of care and service they and
OL,10,Ftheir loved ones deserved, and rightly
OL,11,Fexpected, in relation to the burial of
OL,12,Ftheir loved ones' ashes.
OL,14,F"They were let down at a time when
OL,15,Fthey needed the high level of
OL,16,Fdedication and professionalism that
OL,17,Four crematorium team has always been
OL,18,Fproud to provide.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/7
