OL,3,CCriminal investigation into disposal
OL,4,Cof ashes at crematorium
OL,6,F"I have personally visited or spoken
OL,7,Fto the six families identified as
OL,8,Fbeing directly affected by this
OL,9,Fsituation, to work out how we can best
OL,10,Fhelp them through this difficult time
OL,11,Fand to offer our deepest apologies."
OL,13,FPlans were being made for "lasting
OL,14,Ftributes" to those affected, she said.
OL,16,FThe crematorium is continuing to
OL,17,Foperate as normal with "experienced
OL,18,Findustry professionals" brought in to
OL,19,Frun it.
