OL,6,FMs Andrews added: "I would like to
OL,7,Freassure those who have previously
OL,8,Fused the crematorium that there is no
OL,9,Fevidence of any other families being
OL,10,Faffected."
OL,12,FCh Supt Kate Anderson, of Lincolnshire
OL,13,FPolice, said: "We know what a
OL,14,Fdistressing case this will be for the
OL,15,Ffamily affected, and they are the
OL,16,Fpeople we are keeping in our minds as
OL,17,Fwe progress this investigation.
