OL,6,F"We also realise how upsetting it will
OL,7,Fbe for others who have lost loved ones
OL,8,Fto hear about this investigation, and
OL,9,Fwe are doing everything we can to
OL,10,Fbuild the broader picture of
OL,11,Funderstanding around what has
OL,12,Fhappened, and our officers continue to
OL,13,Fexamine all the circumstances around
OL,14,Fthis case."
OL,16,FThe case is not linked to an
OL,17,Finvestigation into Legacy Independent
OL,18,FFuneral Directors in Hull.
OL,20,FPeople are being asked not to attend
OL,21,Fthe crematorium if they have concerns.
